text: Dmytro Kostyantynovych Semenov (; born 4 November 1999) is a Ukrainian football player who plays for FK Jelgava. ==Club career== He made his Ukrainian Second League debut for FC Dnipro on 15 July 2017 in a game against FC Real Pharma Odesa. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1999 births Category:Sportspeople from Dnipro Category:Living people Category:Ukrainian footballers Category:Ukrainian expatriate footballers Category:Association football defenders Category:FC Dnipro players Category:FC Oleksandriya players Category:MFC Mykolaiv players Category:FK Jelgava players Category:Expatriate footballers in Latvia Category:Ukrainian expatriate sportspeople in Latvia
